### DeletedAddrLabelsNeedingEmission {#a5569c64e0b01ae64bf4328610c56ccd4}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>DenseMap&lt;AssertingVH&lt;Function&gt;, std::vector&lt;MCSymbol &#42;&gt; &gt; llvm::AddrLabelMap::DeletedAddrLabelsNeedingEmission</>}>
This is a per-function list of symbols whose corresponding <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/basicblock">BasicBlock</a> got deleted.

These symbols need to be emitted at some point in the file, so <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/asmprinter">AsmPrinter</a> emits them after the function body.
